2. Why Stacks? The Blockchain Behind the Program

The program focuses on Stacks because it is the leading smart contract layer for Bitcoin.

Stacks enables:

Clarity smart contracts

Bitcoin-secured settlement

sBTC (upcoming trust-minimized Bitcoin for smart contracts)

Web3 apps anchored to Bitcoin

NFTs, DAOs, DeFi, and identity projects

The Stacks Program helps Talent Protocol users navigate these technologies with simple step-by-step missions.
